nights of cabiria ( italian : le notti di cabiria ) is a 1957 italian drama film directed by federico fellini and starring giulietta masina , françois périer , and amedeo nazzari .   based on a story by fellini , the film is about a prostitute in rome who searches for true love in vain .   nights of cabiria won the 1957 academy award for best foreign language film .   this was the second straight year italy and fellini won this academy award , having won for 1956 's la strada , which also starred giulietta masina .